summary: My top 3 favorite episodes of Doctor Who
body:
My top 3 favorite episodes of Doctor Who

1) Midnight

It’s so scary!


2) Blink


In my opinion, the Weeping Angels were so much scary when all they did was send you back in time.


3) The Girl in the Fireplace


Although I will forever ship Ten and Rose, I loved the interaction between Madame de Pompadour and Ten. This episode was so beautiful. Also the music is terrific!



Here are some extras that I found:
